{"tid":1564003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【831太子站】有無可能向消防處索取一份正式事故報告？","createTime":"2019-09-12T15:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:01:49.000Z","uid":299387,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3dfbd9e517ed399ad207529b38f0ea04ffc384dd","tid":1564003,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:14:08.000Z","msg":"睇完消防處今日個記召，再綜合今晚既幾個Post:<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>［HA請解畫］831醫院記錄 顯示10位傷者安排送院情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ahiCOmU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ahiCOmU</a></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>[真相再浮現?] 消防同證人可能都冇講大話！但有神秘假消防抬走嘔白泡傷者！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563130</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗大家都傾向相信消防00:41無數錯，係01:02個陣先因為某d原因改做7個。<br />\n<code>&ldquo;消防：我地見唔到嘅嘢，我地唔估。&rdquo;</code><br />\n<br />\n自問對急救有少少認識，而我相信急救既規矩應該全世界都差唔多，除左救人之餘一定要紀錄底過程同傷勢，就算個PAO無色卡都要有紙或者其他野去record，因為之後一定要寫返份Incident Report。所以其實00:41數到10個傷者好難會錯，急救紀錄（即係你地見到有兩個人仔圖個張）要填傷者呼吸/ 脈搏/ 皮膚顏色/ 瞳孔，檢查完呢d野你話認唔到傷者個樣？而傷者而由Red轉其他顏色更加無可能，因為都係個句，急救一定要紀錄底成個過程，如果傷勢好轉一定要mark底幾點好轉。<br />\n<br />\n好喇提到Incident Report，最基本既資料包括 <span style=\"color: red;\">Casualty Details, What Happened (a brief description) 同 First Aid Action Taken</span>，我當&quot;傷者資料&quot;係個人私隱，咁其他大部份內容都上哂報紙，應該唔係私隱喇掛。（利申：我唔係非法律界人士，有錯請指出）<br />\n<br />\n係消防處既網頁內，公開資料個頁入面，有個位可以比市民申請 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">事故報告</span>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfsd.gov.hk/chi/access/incident_report.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfsd.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Faccess%2Fincident_report.html&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=5a219594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfsd.gov.hk/chi/access/incident_report.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QEfYoqo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQEfYoqo.jpg&h=457bacbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再次重申，我唔係讀法律，希望有法律巴絲可以幫手，當然我自己都有做過功課問過識法律既朋友先上黎開post。基本上記者會所講既野唔係法律證供，要上到court咁佢地講既野先係證供，所以班政客先會成日係電視上面講大話，而d高層亦都日日上電視9up。但據我所知，「事故報告」係全世界大部份地方都係legal document（應該包括香港），而作為First Aider係有legal duty去填呢份報告，所以同Press Con唔同，事故報告係唔可以老作。<br />\n<br />\n如果可以有當日在場人士/ 記者朋友幫手去申請，當然仲好，但其實如果我話我個晚曾經路經太子，消防又點樣證明我唔係呢？當然消防處有權拒絕大家既申請，但正如大家一路叫黨鐵交CCTV佢都唔交，我只係想睇下有無另一條路可以試下。<br />\n<br />\n消防處既高層，我衷心希望你地可以交一份有法律效力既正式事故報告比大家。<br />\n黑警黎緊幾代都會係香港人眼中既過街老鼠，身為紀律部隊，無視法律，完全唔顧市民既性命財產，呢班人死不足惜。但正如今日記者會所講，消防員係冒住生命危險為市民服務，市民對你地既尊重係因為你地過去既表現，you can't demand respect - you have to earn It。無論政見如何，我都相信你地今日係記者會好誠懇咁講個句：「我地絕對唔會見死不救」。多謝你地今日示範左咩係公務員應有既記召水準，更加多謝各位前線消防員既付出，你地絕對係香港市民心目中既英雄。<br />\n<br />\n補充：繼早幾日睇WhatsApp T&amp;C睇到眼殘，我今次都有特登睇埋政府《公開資料守則》，暫時睇唔到同&quot;事故報告&quot;相關既限制。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>【鍵盤戰士請入】向WhatsApp投訴黑警&quot;非官方商業帳號&quot;舉報熱線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ahcwxfU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ahcwxfU</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n政府《公開資料守則》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.access.gov.hk/filemanager/content/codeonacctoinfo/code.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.access.gov.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Fcontent%2Fcodeonacctoinfo%2Fcode.pdf&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=151232f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.access.gov.hk/filemanager/content/codeonacctoinfo/code.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n我亦都順手睇左黑警同消防既網站新聞稿，佢地無寫過831件事既詳情：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfsd.gov.hk/chi/publications/pressrelease/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfsd.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fpublications%2Fpressrelease%2F&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=266768fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfsd.gov.hk/chi/publications/pressrelease/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/03_police_message/pr/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F03_police_message%2Fpr%2Findex.php&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=d1ab5049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/03_police_message/pr/index.php</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，我好想幫忙，但我其實同大家有時差... 希望各位睇睇呢條路可唔可行，歡迎討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  等光復香港之日，我會返黎同大家煲底相見。"},{"pid":"c0cb86a703990bef4aa5b023b8276c8459ab5a8e","tid":1564003,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"[文長][中期檢討]希望大家入黎睇下我地現有既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a8d0c6af539166db008512e06d0385b7d3497b67","tid":1564003,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:14:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"09e57d134efc4dee0ae28b81ae39dea5cdea03b8","tid":1564003,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/a5/a5c603334c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2Fa5%2Fa5c603334c.jpeg&h=b13a8b01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d66b76bdb776c798e2801c972695092838cee843","tid":1564003,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:16:51.000Z","msg":"P牌無力一推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a880ec648a209d1a2c7ed710008feffaece169d3","tid":1564003,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:17:32.000Z","msg":"究竟我幾時先可以甩P牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0959957cdb14d466e5d5da181918edd86a060de7","tid":1564003,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e34c28c0cad1e24a6493df4e21923bdb82b78c6","tid":1564003,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"我知篇文好長.. 但我唔想陣間一堆人又叫我fact check，我上網搵哂資料問左識法律既朋友先閒post咖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望大家唔好介意"},{"pid":"f7d850566f1154a2d84501b4d65e965cbd78ce44","tid":1564003,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:21:22.000Z","msg":"P牌默默地推.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9a7bb193e5018b988502e87b5c53fd35810e50","tid":1564003,"uid":180097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7d850566f1154a2d84501b4d65e965cbd78ce44","tid":1564003,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:21:22.000Z","msg":"P牌默默地推.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"幫下你"},{"pid":"da7e6774afe8613a863b7815c73abfbb18d4c175","tid":1564003,"uid":180097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc9a7bb193e5018b988502e87b5c53fd35810e50","tid":1564003,"uid":180097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7d850566f1154a2d84501b4d65e965cbd78ce44","tid":1564003,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:21:22.000Z","msg":"P牌默默地推.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"幫下你"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:23:17.000Z","msg":"我唔識呢啲<br />\n但都推